issue.title: [Feature] LaTeX table generator
issue.body:
Something I often do when using PySR in papers is create a table of all generated equations with their complexities and losses. 

It would be great if PySR had a feature to do this automatically, with some desired precision of constants, and some sub-selection of equations. 

(It would also be nice if PySR could automatically generate plots of predicted vs true for some subselection of equations.)
